Ideen von Chatti auf denen wir aufbauen können


1. Energieproduktion und -konsum
1.	Vergleich der Energieproduktion pro Land mit deren Konsum:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, SUM(renewablesProduction) AS TotalProduction, 
       SUM(renewablesConsumption) AS TotalConsumption,
       (SUM(renewablesProduction) - SUM(renewablesConsumption)) AS NetBalance
FROM renewablesProduction
JOIN renewablesConsumption USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING NetBalance > 0; -- Länder mit Produktionsüberschuss
2.	Ermittlung der Länder mit der höchsten Abhängigkeit von Energieimporten:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, (energyImport / (energyImport + energyProduction)) * 100 AS DependencyRate
FROM energyTrade
JOIN country USING (countryCode)
WHERE year = 2020
ORDER BY DependencyRate DESC
LIMIT 10;
3.	Korrelation zwischen Energieintensität und Wirtschaftswachstum:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, AVG(energyIntensity) AS AvgEnergyIntensity, AVG(gdp_growth) AS AvgGDPGrowth
FROM energyEfficiency
JOIN economy USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING AVG(gdp_growth) > 0
ORDER BY AvgEnergyIntensity ASC;
________________________________________
2. Erneuerbare Energien
4.	Länder mit dem höchsten Anteil erneuerbarer Energien an der Gesamtenergieproduktion:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, 
       (SUM(renewablesProduction) / (SUM(renewablesProduction) + energyProduction)) * 100 AS RenewablesShare
FROM renewablesProduction
JOIN energyTrade USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
ORDER BY RenewablesShare DESC
LIMIT 10;
5.	Anteil von Solar- vs. Windenergie in den letzten 5 Jahren (pro Land):
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, year, 
       SUM(Solar) AS TotalSolar, SUM(Wind) AS TotalWind,
       (SUM(Solar) / (SUM(Solar) + SUM(Wind))) * 100 AS SolarShare,
       (SUM(Wind) / (SUM(Solar) + SUM(Wind))) * 100 AS WindShare
FROM renewablesProduction
GROUP BY countryName, year
HAVING year >= 2015;
6.	Trends in der Solarenergieproduktion über die letzten 10 Jahre:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT year, SUM(Solar) AS TotalSolarProduction
FROM renewablesProduction
GROUP BY year
ORDER BY year ASC;
________________________________________
3. Emissionen
7.	Länder mit den höchsten CO₂-Emissionen im Vergleich zu ihrem Anteil an erneuerbaren Energien:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, SUM(CO2Emissions) AS TotalCO2, 
       AVG(percentageRenew) AS AvgRenewablesShare
FROM emissions
JOIN shareRenewables USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING TotalCO2 > 500 AND AvgRenewablesShare < 20; -- Filter für hohe Emissionen und geringe erneuerbare Anteile
8.	Vergleich von Methan- und CO₂-Emissionen über Kontinente:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT continent, SUM(CO2Emissions) AS TotalCO2, SUM(methaneEmissions) AS TotalMethane
FROM emissions
JOIN encompasses USING (countryCode)
GROUP BY continent;
________________________________________
4. Energieeffizienz
9.	Länder mit der besten Energieeffizienz pro Wirtschaftssektor (Agrar, Industrie, Service):
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, sector, MIN(energyIntensity) AS BestEfficiency
FROM energyEfficiency
JOIN economy USING (countryCode, year)
WHERE sector IN ('Agriculture', 'Industry', 'Service')
GROUP BY countryName, sector;
10.	Trends in der Energieeffizienz in der Europäischen Union:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT year, AVG(energyIntensity) AS AvgEfficiencyEU
FROM energyEfficiency
JOIN encompasses USING (countryCode)
WHERE continent = 'Europe'
GROUP BY year
ORDER BY year ASC;
________________________________________
5. Länderübergreifende Handelsströme
11.	Länder mit dem größten Netto-Energieexport (Export minus Import):
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, (SUM(energyExport) - SUM(energyImport)) AS NetExport
FROM energyTrade
GROUP BY countryName
ORDER BY NetExport DESC
LIMIT 10;
12.	Analyse des Energiehandels zwischen Kontinenten:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT continent, SUM(energyExport) AS TotalExport, SUM(energyImport) AS TotalImport
FROM energyTrade
JOIN encompasses USING (countryCode)
GROUP BY continent;
________________________________________
6. Kombination von Faktoren
13.	Länder mit den höchsten CO₂-Emissionen und geringem Anteil erneuerbarer Energien:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, AVG(CO2Emissions) AS AvgCO2, AVG(percentageRenew) AS AvgRenewables
FROM emissions
JOIN shareRenewables USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING AvgCO2 > 300 AND AvgRenewables < 15;
14.	Vergleich zwischen Entwicklungsländern und Industrienationen in Bezug auf Energieeffizienz:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, AVG(energyIntensity) AS AvgEfficiency, gdp_per_capita
FROM energyEfficiency
JOIN economy USING (countryCode)
WHERE gdp_per_capita > 10000 OR gdp_per_capita < 3000
GROUP BY countryName;
________________________________________
7. Langfristige Trends
15.	Trends in der Produktion erneuerbarer Energien über 10 Jahre:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT year, SUM(Wind + Solar + GeoBiomass) AS RenewablesProduction
FROM renewablesProduction
GROUP BY year
ORDER BY year ASC;
16.	Analyse des Anteils erneuerbarer Energien in Ländern mit steigender Bevölkerung:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, AVG(percentageRenew) AS AvgRenewables, population_growth
FROM shareRenewables
JOIN countryPop USING (countryCode)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING population_growth > 1;
17.	Analyse von Handelsströmen in Ländern mit hohen Methan-Emissionen:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, SUM(energyExport) AS TotalExport, SUM(methaneEmissions) AS Methane
FROM energyTrade
JOIN emissions USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY countryName
HAVING Methane > 50;
________________________________________
8. Globale Vergleiche
18.	Top 10 Länder mit dem höchsten Solar-Anteil an erneuerbarer Energieproduktion:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, (SUM(Solar) / SUM(Solar + Wind + Hydro)) * 100 AS SolarShare
FROM renewablesProduction
GROUP BY countryName
ORDER BY SolarShare DESC
LIMIT 10;
19.	Vergleich von Emissionen und Handelsströmen für G20-Länder:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT countryName, SUM(CO2Emissions) AS TotalEmissions, 
       SUM(energyImport) AS TotalImport, SUM(energyExport) AS TotalExport
FROM emissions
JOIN energyTrade USING (countryCode, year)
WHERE countryName IN ('USA', 'China', 'Germany', ...); -- G20-Länder
20.	Analyse des Anstiegs erneuerbarer Energien im Vergleich zu fossilen Brennstoffen:
sql
Code kopieren
SELECT year, SUM(renewablesProduction) AS TotalRenewables, 
       SUM(energyProduction - renewablesProduction) AS FossilProduction
FROM renewablesProduction
JOIN energyTrade USING (countryCode, year)
GROUP BY year
ORDER BY year ASC;
